snippet: Pakistan captain Misbah-ul-Haq will contemplate his playing future prior to the third test against Australia and is not ruling out retirement after leading Pakistan to an innings and 18-run defeat on Friday....
lead_paragraph: Pakistan captain Misbah-ul-Haq will contemplate his playing future prior to the third test against Australia and is not ruling out retirement after leading Pakistan to an innings and 18-run defeat on Friday.

headline.main: Pakistan Captain Misbah Ponders Playing Future
headline.print_headline: Pakistan Captain Misbah Ponders Playing Future
